 Galvatron and Magnus flew at eachother at a certain point. It was an open 
valley of green. The two set on one spot. Both at full speed. Magnus showed 
his gun. Gakvatron showed his teeth. At the middle point where the two would 
meet sparks started to fly. They hit full force and both landed 5 feet 
backwards from eachother. The two stared eachother down. Galvatron 
stated..."You have something I want."
  "You wont get it except my foot in your waste disposal unit!"
  Galvatron snarled..."I will destroy you with my bare hands!"
  With that they where off Galvatron shot of his flame energy while Magnus 
shot off a couuple of gun fire shots. The fight is on!

--part1_8e.107587f8.27a8c1a5_boundary
